results.description: It's Tony Stark's worst nightmare! In a fevered dream-like state, Iron Man faces what he fears the most: his technology running rampant -- causing world war, death and destruction -- and it's all his fault! Will Tony turn back to the bottle or let the technology take control? See Iron Man vs. his greatest enemy: himself!
